WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:02.835
♪♪

00:04.371 --> 00:09.608
<i> ♪ Welcome to my wicked world,</i>
<i> wicked world ♪</i>

00:13.180 --> 00:15.480
Wait! So you're telling me
I could play a sport

00:15.515 --> 00:18.383
where I get rewarded
for stealing a base?

00:18.418 --> 00:20.285
I swear on my mother's coat.

00:23.723 --> 00:26.258
Ugh, I cannot believe this is
what I've been reduced to.

00:32.099 --> 00:34.366
Daah!
What are you doing here?

00:34.401 --> 00:37.502
Following you.
You're up to no good,
and I want in.

00:37.537 --> 00:39.738
Okay, Freddie,
it's not even like, evil.

00:39.773 --> 00:41.239
You'd be way bored.

00:41.274 --> 00:44.076
Jacking a limo,
sneaking onto
the Isle of the Lost,

00:44.111 --> 00:46.711
stealing a jewel!
(laughs) Let's do this!

00:46.746 --> 00:48.447
You were not
just following me,

00:48.482 --> 00:50.282
you were listening, too!

00:50.317 --> 00:55.387
Guilty.
Just can't trust us VKs.

00:55.422 --> 00:57.589
GPS voice:
<i> Approaching destination.</i>

00:57.624 --> 01:00.559
<i> Protective dome disengaged.</i>

01:02.329 --> 01:06.465
Mal:
(sigh)
Home, freak home.

01:06.500 --> 01:07.532
Now, where do we start?

01:07.567 --> 01:10.469
My dad hid things
for just about everyone.

01:10.504 --> 01:12.370
Even for the worst
of the worst.

01:12.405 --> 01:13.738
That is my mom.

01:13.773 --> 01:16.441
Okay, so we get in,
find that jewel,

01:16.476 --> 01:18.543
and get out
before anyone sees us.

01:18.578 --> 01:20.345
Sounds like a plan.

01:21.515 --> 01:23.615
Let the searching begin!

01:23.650 --> 01:25.684
♪ ♪

01:27.154 --> 01:29.721
Ew! Monkey hair.

01:29.756 --> 01:31.323
-(gasps)
-(Mal laughs)

01:31.358 --> 01:33.092
(Freddie laughs)

01:34.327 --> 01:37.429
-Ugh!
-Uh... sorry.

01:39.432 --> 01:41.333
No jewel in here.

01:42.802 --> 01:45.437
Ooh, I like this.
(laughs)

01:45.472 --> 01:47.572
Any luck?

01:47.607 --> 01:50.142
Nah... you?

01:50.177 --> 01:51.210
Nah.

01:52.212 --> 01:54.479
Cool.

01:54.514 --> 01:56.982
-Ta-da!
(laughs)
-Whoa!

01:57.017 --> 01:58.550
Okay.

02:00.487 --> 02:02.221
Aah!

02:03.223 --> 02:07.025
-Ahh...
-Wha... whoa,
whoa, whoa!

02:07.060 --> 02:08.093
Woo!

02:08.128 --> 02:09.194
(giggling)

02:09.229 --> 02:11.429
Do you think your dad's
gonna notice we were here?

02:11.464 --> 02:14.333
-Nah.
-(both laughing)

02:15.535 --> 02:17.636
Sorry you didn't
find your jewel, Mal.

02:18.705 --> 02:21.339
But here. This lucky necklace
is all yours.

02:21.374 --> 02:22.507
From me to you.

02:22.542 --> 02:23.875
Oh. Thanks, Freddie.

02:23.910 --> 02:26.311
Guess we'd better
head back.

02:26.346 --> 02:28.446
(sighs)
Yeah.

02:28.481 --> 02:29.681
Huh?

02:29.716 --> 02:31.917
(laughs evilly)
